``` r
library(ggplot2)
theme_set(theme_bw())
library(twitteR)
library(purrr)
library(dplyr)
library(stringr)

setup_twitter_oauth(api_key,api_secret,access_token,access_token_secret)
```

``` r
tweets <- searchTwitter("Paterno", n=5000) %>%
  map_df(as.data.frame)
```
